Synopsis:
    hotlist [nick][-nick][-remove nick]

Description:
    Hotlist entries are used like a notify on irc. It most closely resembles
    dalnet's watch list. Nicks with a leading - require either a double --
    or use of the -remove flag.

Examples:
    To add a nick:
         /hotlist pana
    To remove a nick:
         /hotlist -pana
         /hotlist -remove pana
    To display your hotlist nicks:
         /hotlist


